{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers in diverse fields have begun to focus on large models.",
    "Several researchers in the field of biology have studied large-scale question-and-answer models.",
    "For example, in the medical field, Hong Kong Chinese (Shenzhen) launched \"Hua Tuo,\" etc., this series of research has focused everyone's attention on large-language model development.",
    "If the DTI prediction problem can be combined with the excellent reasoning and prediction capabilities of large-language models, the ability of the DTI prediction model may be significantly improved.",
    "Therefore, future research may start from the data itself, integrate and align the collected data, standardize data representation, and improve the sample screening and construction division of the dataset."
